<html t:type="layout" xmlns:t="http://tapestry.apache.org/schema/tapestry_5_1_0.xsd" xmlns:p="tapestry:parameter">
    
    <section id="presentation">
    	<p>Wooki is a fantastic tool to write and publish documents with the possibility of letting others reviewing it.</p>
    	<p>Read them directly on the website, as a PDF ebook, or on your SmartPhone. We really want to make your writing as accessible as possible. </p>
    	
    	<p id="signup">
    		<a href="#">Signup in 30 seconds.<br />
    		<em>Create and review documents now</em></a>
    	</p>
    	
    </section>
    
    <section id="book-feed" class="activity-feed">
        <h1>Fresh stuff</h1>
        <ol>
        	<t:loop source="freshStuffs" value="current">
        	<li>
                ${current.bookTitle} <em>${current.action} </em> <a href="#">${current.username}</a> <em> ${current.period}</em>
            </li>
            </t:loop>
        </ol>
    </section>
    
    <section id="user-feed" class="activity-feed">
        <h1>Last users activity</h1>
        <ol>
            <li>
                <a href="#">ccordenier</a> <em> just joined wooki</em>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="#">gg</a> <em> has posted a comment on </em> <a href="#">Ride Rails</a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="#">robink</a> <em> just joined wooki</em>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </section>
</html>
